{"tid":1011091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Amazon 即日起支援繁體中文","createTime":"2019-02-06T13:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T13:17:48.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4409c0eb650ed66275fd3020acbf55b35ceaec4","tid":1011091,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"過年領紅包打算怎麼花了嗎？或許跨海買買 Amazon 是好選擇。Amazon（美國）即日起支援繁體中文，還依照消費者所在位置，自動推播可配送至台灣的商品！<br />\n<br />\n以美版迷你超級任天堂 SFC 為例，原售價為 105 美金再加上 AamzonGlobal、進口費用押金為 119.26 美金，折合台幣約 3,668 元，已比 Momo 售價便宜許多、比 PChome24h便宜一些。另外在台灣 Google 官方商城還未上架的 Pixel Slate 也買得到。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，Amazon 也公佈了配送至台灣的物流價格（實際以結帳為主），以編輯試買Anova Culinary A2.2-120V-US 藍芽舒肥機為例，從肯塔基州發貨的話 AmazonGlobal的運費加報關費用為 15.48 美元。<br />\n<br />\n不過要注意的是，之前國人也很愛買的 Amazon 日本尚未支援繁體中文，另外Amazon 美國也尚未支援台灣電子書販售。"},{"pid":"e845db94da9f2cefa98d1a43959aadfa565f92d1","tid":1011091,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23f6386535a4740366f5096811ca0beb8077f18","tid":1011091,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"93992c296a082e05dc5a1f08be0a324b109a4932","tid":1011091,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"Google translate only"},{"pid":"16bc17921a29a233b6c7cd85a622c92d7bb6d9b5","tid":1011091,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93992c296a082e05dc5a1f08be0a324b109a4932","tid":1011091,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"Google translate only"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"唔通你期望全部賣家一夜學識中文<br />\n用流利中文打description咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}